  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>You create a cluster of glowing darts of magical force. The missiles animate and hurtle through the air, unerringly seeking their target.</em></p><p>This spell is completely negated by the<em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.k6lJOHWJa0XF2zCb]{Shield}</em>spell.</p><p><strong>Always Hits</strong> </p><p>Hits three times, which can be split between targets when casting.</p><ul><li><p>Target takes [[/damage 1d4+1 force]] damage for each missile.<strong>*</strong> </p></li></ul><p><em>If you strike the same target multiple times and your target needs to make a concentration check, only roll once for the combined damage. This spell also doesn't cause more than one death saving throw failure when striking a creature with 0 hit points multiple times.</em></p><p></p><p><strong>*Upcasting:</strong> Add one missile ([[/damage 1d4+1 force]]{1d4+1 force damage}) for each spell level above 1st.</p>",
